description:
Sardis - the fifth of the seven Churches of Revelation is located on the road to Philadelphia. It sits below some stunning mountain scenery and today the city is abandoned and desolate - a fitting fulfilment of a church that is described as being dead. There is some fascinating history connected to this church with powerful lessons for us today. Do you struggle with dead formalism and need a revival in your spiritual life? May this message motivate and revive you.
